Yeah, well,
that's pretty much not in the cards.

01:19:22.160 --> 01:19:24.390
I decided against the science

01:19:24.880 --> 01:19:28.111
and it seems time
finally caught up with me.

01:19:29.760 --> 01:19:33.719
