But, um...

01:22:04.640 --> 01:22:06.995
Just so you know, tomorrow's a half-day.

01:22:08.400 --> 01:22:09.992
Well, I'll be here then.

01:22:29.920 --> 01:22:30.989
Hey.

01:22:34.040 --> 01:22:35.553
Here you are.

01:22:37.280 --> 01:22:41.239
